tool_description:
TikTok API.
Using it, you can get the following.
signature, no watermark video,tiktok stories,trending feed by region, user info, user post video, user following list, hot video list, hot challenge list, comment list by video, search video, search user…
name: tiktok download
title: tiktok download

api_list.name: ping
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://tiktok-download5.p.rapidapi.com/ping"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "tiktok-download5.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
